      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "<b><color=red>RULES:</b></color>\n<b><color=red>1. </b></color>During
    MIDNIGHT PARTY, when your balance is less than $1, add funds through your agent.
    \n<b><color=red>2. </b></color>After adding funds, the system will prompt you
    whether to participate in the MIDNIGHT PARTY event. Select \"YES\" and the system
    will automatically match you demosit(Deposited $100 + $100 Bonus), if you select
    \"NO\", you will not participate in the event.\n<b><color=red>3. </b></color>
    CASH OUT: Your balance must reach 5x of your total deposit. Which is if it's
    $100 demosited and you get $100 MIDNIGHT PARTY bonus; $200 is your total deposit
    and you ticket out at $1000\"."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: f5c62f78d979dbc4b85dd681db334fff, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: -2327674942082310918, guid: f5c62f78d979dbc4b85dd681db334fff, type: 2}
